# Embedded SPA dist (step 5) is NOT gitignored: //go:embed reads
# files at compile time, so they must be present in the working
# tree. The Makefile's STAGE_DASHBOARD_DIST_CMD copies
# web/dashboard/dist/ into internal/api/web/dist/ before go build.
# In CI, `make build` runs the stage command automatically.
